{"name": "odoo14-addon-ssi-partner-public-offering", "metadata": {"name": "odoo14-addon-ssi-partner-public-offering", "version": "14.0.1.0.0", "classifiers": ["Framework :: Odoo", "Framework :: Odoo :: 14.0", "License :: OSI Approved :: GNU Affero General Public License v3", "Programming Language :: Python"], "home_page": "https://simetri-sinergi.id", "license": "AGPL-3", "documentation_url": null, "dependencies": ["odoo14-addon-ssi-master-data-mixin", "odoo14-addon-ssi-partner", "odoo"], "summary": "Company Partner's Public Offering Information", "upload_time": 1716764931}, "documentation": ["```{image} https://img.shields.io/badge/licence-AGPL--3-blue.svg\n:alt: 'License: AGPL-3'\n:target: http://www.gnu.org/licenses/agpl-3.0-standalone.html\n```\n\n# Company Partner's Public Offering Information\n\n## Installation\n\nTo install this module, you need to:\n\n1. Clone the branch 14.0 of the repository <https://github.com/open-synergy/ssi-partner>\n2. Add the path to this repository in your configuration (addons-path)\n3. Update the module list\n4. Go to menu *Setting -> Modules -> Local Modules*\n5. Search For *Company Partner's Public Offering Information*\n6. Install the module\n\n## Bug Tracker\n\nBugs are tracked on [GitHub Issues](https://github.com/open-synergy/ssi-partner/issues).\nIn case of trouble, please check there if your issue has already been reported.\nIf you spotted it first, help us smashing it by providing a detailed\nand welcomed feedback.\n\n## Credits\n\n### Contributors\n\n- Michael Viriyananda \\<<mailto:viriyananda.michael@gmail.com>>\n- Andhitia Rama \\<<mailto:andhitia.r@gmail.com>>\n\n### Maintainer\n\n```{image} https://simetri-sinergi.id/logo.png\n:alt: PT. Simetri Sinergi Indonesia\n:target: https://simetri-sinergi.id.com\n```\n\nThis module is maintained by the PT. Simetri Sinergi Indonesia.\n"], "modules": [{"name": "odoo.addons.ssi_partner_public_offering.models.company_public_offering_type", "documentation": ["Copyright 2023 OpenSy